SUBSCRIBE & ADOPT A KATANA WITH THE LINK IN BIO!! 

If you love katana unboxing, then you'll love this. See the Katanas slice in action as satisfying as ASMR! These aren't rusted katanas! Sword-making, blacksmithing, knife making, and katana making are Mini Katana's passions! If you love anime like One Piece, Naruto, Demon Slayer, Attack on Titan, Miira No Kaikata, Mugen Train, Jujutsu Kaisen, sword art online abridged, slice of life anime, chainsaw man vs katana, afro samurai and are excited about the Swordsmith arc, you're gonna love our ninja weapons! Mini Katana is the founding titan of katana making, knife making, and the mini katana keychain. Learn how to draw a katana and how to make kunai like Naruto. We are the last samurai. We love Japanese anime, Japanese history, Japanese lofi, Japanese movies, and Japanese songs. Subscribe to watch mini katana unboxing, how to make a katana with cardboard and with paper, and more!  The Mini Katana Store is committed to high quality carbon steel blades and giving you slice of life looks as we try not to laugh challenge. Trust, Mini Katana knows how to make kunai and how to make a sword!

snippet.title: BINI | 'Blink Twice' Official Music Video
snippet.description:
#BINI : ‚ÄòBlink Twice‚Äô is a fun pop song about trying to figure out if your crush likes you back. With a catchy beat and relatable lyrics, it captures the excitement and confusion of waiting for a sign- like a simple blink- to know if they feel the same. 

Stream #BINI_BlinkTwice now on all platforms: https://orcd.co/bini_blinktwice 

I heard you like confidence
Well I‚Äôve got a lot of it
So baby use common sense
Just don‚Äôt be anonymous
I heard that you‚Äôve been busy
Yeah I heard it through the grapevine
Trying my best not to step up on your land mine
But let‚Äôs have some fun with it
Cause you know I‚Äôm running it

Ooh ooh
I‚Äôm lost inside your world
You got that symphony
Like da doo da doo da doo

If you like me blink twice
Are you naughty or nice
Maybe add a little spice
If you‚Äôre tryna roll the dice
Let me give you some advice
If you like me blink twice
Uh oh

Ooh ooh 
He‚Äôs not even thinkin‚Äô bout me
Ooh ooh 
Maybe he‚Äôs just lookin‚Äô at me

Got me goin‚Äô crazy
Baby no don‚Äôt be lazy
Come over and chase me
Yeah you better amaze me
I‚Äôm at the spot
Baby tell me are you
Ready or not
Don‚Äôt you leave me waitin‚Äô

If you, you really like me
Baby then just blink twice
If you, you really like me
Then you gotta roll the dice
